e87e1a62-d8a2-4149-823b-e1dc226e402a.title: Wyson
e87e1a62-d8a2-4149-823b-e1dc226e402a.text:
If I'm not mistaken, you've got some body parts from a
big mole there! I'll trade it for bird nests if ye likes. Or
was ye wantin' some woad leaves instead?

options.text: Okay, I will trade the mole parts.
Yes please, I need woad leaves.

73e743f1-1ae9-4f0d-a516-6b17e64712ad.title: <player>
73e743f1-1ae9-4f0d-a516-6b17e64712ad.text: Okay, I will trade the mole parts.

d090fd7a-80d3-4c52-8090-2dac068835a1.title: Wyson
d090fd7a-80d3-4c52-8090-2dac068835a1.text:
I'm the head gardener around here.
If you're looking for woad leaves, or if you need help
with owt, I'm yer man.

options.text: Yes please, I need woad leaves.
How about ME helping YOU instead?

3ed6e613-01d7-4315-9f41-687f91fb4def.title: <player>
3ed6e613-01d7-4315-9f41-687f91fb4def.text: Yes please, I need woad leaves.

c153c640-c137-4c11-87b2-3aed34459b68.title: Wyson
c153c640-c137-4c11-87b2-3aed34459b68.text: How much are you willing to pay?

67ddd8d1-1b10-4da1-8e88-f3faae67a4ae.title: Wyson
67ddd8d1-1b10-4da1-8e88-f3faae67a4ae.text:
No no, that's far too little. Woad leaves are hard to get.
I used to have plenty but someone kept stealing them
off me.

40f44fa6-345d-4e0f-a22f-9b5037789ec7.title: Wyson
40f44fa6-345d-4e0f-a22f-9b5037789ec7.text: I'll be around if you have any more gardening needs.

ddd54adf-4f1f-4bd6-9f59-247173493ffe.title: <player>
ddd54adf-4f1f-4bd6-9f59-247173493ffe.text:
I don't have enough coins to buy the leaves.
I'll come back later.

1275f13d-9a24-4c2a-8ea1-62f28a31f361.title: Wyson
1275f13d-9a24-4c2a-8ea1-62f28a31f361.text: Here, have two, you're a generous person.

c0dd7a84-a7e7-45cb-9c23-b6565bf8aaba.title: <player>
c0dd7a84-a7e7-45cb-9c23-b6565bf8aaba.text: How about ME helping YOU instead?

ce74bb2f-be24-4c9c-9fc1-0d68de5f0757.title: Wyson
ce74bb2f-be24-4c9c-9fc1-0d68de5f0757.text:
That's a nice thing to say. I do need a hand, now you
mention it. You see, there's some stupid mole digging
up my lovely garden.

e1c57a80-7785-43f3-a904-79c50e80f246.title: <player>
e1c57a80-7785-43f3-a904-79c50e80f246.text: A mole? Surely you've dealt with moles in the past?

3b05400c-b45b-4ae7-9455-aedae75c5ee3.title: Wyson
3b05400c-b45b-4ae7-9455-aedae75c5ee3.text:
Ah, well this is no ordinary mole! He's a big'un for
sure. Ya see... I'm always relied upon to make the most
of this 'ere garden - the faster and bigger I can grow
plants the better!

d3373c68-a4bb-4dbe-abf2-279011ebfd63.title: Wyson
d3373c68-a4bb-4dbe-abf2-279011ebfd63.text:
In my quest for perfection I looked into 'Malignius-
Mortifer's-Super-Ultra-Flora-Growth-Potion'. It worked
well on my plants, no doubt about it! But it had the
same effect on a nearby mole. Ya can imagine the

561f7b2c-ecb3-4664-84fb-4c8f5c693958.title: Wyson
561f7b2c-ecb3-4664-84fb-4c8f5c693958.text:
havoc he causes to my patches of sunflowers! Why, if
any of the other gardeners knew about this mole, I'd be
looking for a new job in no time!

a356020f-b939-43f5-af31-b60d4cd38f1f.title: <player>
a356020f-b939-43f5-af31-b60d4cd38f1f.text: I see. What do you need me to do?

530a9b60-daba-4382-a5f1-3175099e9518.title: Wyson
530a9b60-daba-4382-a5f1-3175099e9518.text:
If ya are willing maybe yer wouldn't mind killing it for
me? Take a spade and use it to shake up them mole
hills. Be careful though, he really is big!

3313e5f3-4577-4c8b-accd-9bbd1305078e.title: <player>
3313e5f3-4577-4c8b-accd-9bbd1305078e.text: Is there anything in this for me?

76abee70-e857-49c1-9f55-d5b11e7acf5e.title: Wyson
76abee70-e857-49c1-9f55-d5b11e7acf5e.text:
Well, if yer gets any mole skin or mole claws off 'un,
I'd trade 'em for bird nests if ye brings 'em here to
me.

d641c944-b30a-4248-8133-cb71540048be.title: <player>
d641c944-b30a-4248-8133-cb71540048be.text: Right, I'll bear it in mind.
